<subSubSection pageId="5" pageNumber="462" type="conservation">
<paragraph blockId="5.[161,1369,285,750]" pageId="5" pageNumber="462">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[163,508,559,588]" pageId="5" pageNumber="462">Status and Conservation.</emphasis>
CITES Appendix II. Classified as Least Concern on The [UCN Red List. The Chestnut-bellied Titi has a relatively large range in a pristine region and there are no major threats known to be affecting it.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
